pingball.util

Class Pair<T,U>

  • java.lang.Object
    • pingball.util.Pair<T,U>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GridLocation

    public class Pair<T,U>
extends java.lang.Object
    An immutable Pair. Pair provides the functionality of an immutable pair of objects. This class does not guarantee immutability when the objects contained within this pair are mutable themselves. Rep-Invariant: None. There is no specific limitation on the value of each object in the pair
